* '''Estate agent:''' Sorry [player name], I'm talking to Oziach right now.
* {{tact|end}}

===Overhearing conversations between Oziach and the Estate agent===
* {{trandom}}
* {{topt|Dialogue 1}}
** '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|Is this place haunted?}}
** {{tact|Estate agent shrugs (emote)}}
** '''Estate agent:''' {{overhead|I don't think so. Would it matter if it was?}}
** {{tact|Oziach thinks (emote)}}
** '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|Maybe, it depends how haunted. I'm not a big fan of ghosts.}}
** '''Estate agent:''' {{overhead|Well, let's hope it's not haunted!}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Dialogue 2}}
** '''Estate agent:''' {{overhead|Have you thought about painting the building?}}
** {{tact|Oziach nods yes (emote)}}
** '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|I'm thinking a nice bold red, like the dragon armour.}}
** '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|Or maybe a green, in memory of Elvarg, a very mean dragon.}}
** {{tact|Estate agent nods yes (emote)}}
** '''Estate agent:''' {{overhead|I think green would look great, it would match the surroundings, too!}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Dialogue 3}}
** '''Estate agent:''' {{overhead|Could I get one of those rune platebodies?}}
** {{tact|Oziach thinks (emote)}}
** '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|Well, normally you'd have to slay a dragon for me...}}
** '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|...but maybe I can make an exception once I've moved in here.}}
** '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|As a little thank you for the help!}}
** {{tact|Estate agent nods yes (emote)}}
** '''Estate agent:''' {{overhead|That would be great! Let's get this deal done quickly.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Dialogue 4}}
** {{tact|Oziach cheers (emote)}}
** '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|I can't wait to complete the purchase!}}
** '''Estate agent:''' {{overhead|It's almost done Oziach, not much longer.}}
** '''Estate agent:''' {{overhead|Do you have any plans for it?}}
** {{tact|Oziach shrugs (emote)}}
** '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|I have a few. I might convert the top floor into a bar!}}
** '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|It'll be for all dragon slayers I know, there's a lot of us!}}
** {{tact|Estate agent laughs (emote)}}
** '''Estate agent:''' {{overhead|Interesting use of such a beautiful property!}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Dialogue 5}}
** '''Estate agent:''' {{overhead|OoooOooOoOoOoooooooo!}}
** {{tact|Oziach is scared (emote)}}
** '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|Ah!! Why did you do that?}}
** '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|That scared me!}}
** '''Estate agent:''' {{overhead|I'm sorry! I was just pretending to be a ghost.}}
** '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|Don't do that! I don't like ghosts.}}
** {{tact|end}}

===Attempting to climb the evergreen tree=== <!--Varbit 13097 == (0 || 5 || 10)-->
