===Cutscene===
* {{qact|A cutscene starts with the player hiding behind an evergreen tree, whilst an estate agent and Oziach speak.}}
* '''Estate agent:''' {{overhead|I'm going to head back to the office.}}
* '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|Alright, I'll see you later. Can't wait to move in!}}
* '''Estate agent:''' {{overhead|I know, it's a lovely place! See you!}}
* {{qact|The estate agent leaves.}}
* '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|Ahhh... soon to be mine.}}
* {{qact|The cutscene ends.}}
* {{tact|continue}}

====After the cutscene ends====
* '''Player:''' Oziach is alone! Seems like the perfect time to scare him.
* '''Player:''' I just need to climb this tree and blow on the bottle, that should do it.
* {{tact|end}}

====Gameplay====
=====If the player destroys the bottle from inventory=====
* {{mes|You destroyed the bottle, meaning you have no way of scaring Oziach anymore.}}<!--Game chat message, doesn't get filtered as spam.-->
* {{qact|{{Map|x=3045|y=3496|type=maplink|text=}}The player returns to Brother Jered.}}<!--Always to coordinates 3045, 3496, 0. Has no effect on Oziach (varbit 13111).-->
<!--There will be no "Oops" message from the player here.-->
* '''Player:''' I should talk to Brother Jered about trying this again.
* {{tact|end}}

=====If the player leaves the instance early=====
* {{qact|{{Map|x=3045|y=3496|type=maplink|text=}}The player returns to Brother Jered.}}<!--Always to coordinates 3045, 3496, 0. Has no effect on Oziach (varbit 13111).-->
* '''Player:''' I should talk to Brother Jered about trying this again.
* {{tact|end}}

=====If the player doesn't climb the tree within 30 seconds or Oziach spots the player=====
* '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|I see you there, what are you doing?!}}
* {{qact|{{Map|x=3045|y=3496|type=maplink|text=}}The player returns to Brother Jered. [[RuneScape:Varbit/13111|Oziach will remember to have caught the player.]]}}<!--Always to coordinates 3045, 3496, 0.-->
* '''Player:''' Oziach caught me. I should try to be a bit faster next time.
* '''Player:''' I should talk to Brother Jered about trying this again.
* {{tact|end}}

=====If the player climbs the tree=====
* '''Player:''' {{overhead|OOOoOOOooOOooOOOOoOOOO}}
* {{qact|The player shakes the evergreen tree slightly.}}
* '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|What was that? A ghost?!}}
* '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|Hello?? Is that a ghost?}}
* '''Oziach:''' {{overhead|ONE ghost? Haha, ONE ghost can't spook me!}}
* {{qact|The player returns to Brother Jered.}}<!--Coordinates wanted for a maplink.-->
* '''Player:''' Seems like I wasn't very scary. Oziach said ONE ghost isn't enough!
* '''Player:''' I need to find another ghost, to scare Oziach from the trees on the other side of the path. That would work!
* '''Player:''' I should talk to Brother Jered about this. Maybe he can help.
* {{tact|end}}

