==Getting an accomplice==
===Talking to Benny after getting an ad coupon===
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Talk about the Halloween event.}}<!-- Varbit 13097 >= 21 && <= 67 -->
** '''Player:''' Hi Benny, I'd like to place an ad please! Specifically an LFG ad.
